rule 1:
Every click should result in a x or o being displayed on the screen


Every click on square should alternatively display x and O 
That once click on square should not 
    -- no consecutive x is allowed
    -- no consecutive o is allowed

win:
    -- When there is are consecutive 3 x horizontally vertically or diagnally
    -- When there is are consecutive 3 o horizontally vertically or diagnally

Game stops when:
    --when there is a win
    --when all the columns and rows are used without winning